OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,FThe technology will mean some people
OL,7,Fwith type 1 diabetes will no longer
OL,8,Fneed to inject themselves with insulin
OL,10,FTens of thousands of children and
OL,11,Fadults living with across England are
OL,12,Fset to receive an "artificial
OL,13,Fpancreas" in a world-first initiative
OL,14,Fbeing rolled out by the NHS.
OL,16,FThe new device, rolled out from
OL,17,FTuesday, continually monitors a
OL,18,Fperson's blood glucose, then
OL,19,Fautomatically adjusts the amount of
OL,20,Finsulin given to them through a pump.
