OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,FIt is said to also help prevent life-
OL,7,Fthreatening hypoglycaemic and
OL,8,Fhyperglycaemia attacks, which can lead
OL,9,Fto seizures, coma, or even death for
OL,10,Fpeople living with type 1 diabetes.
OL,12,FNHS England has provided local health
OL,13,Fsystems with #2.5 million to start
OL,14,Fidentifying patients that can benefit.
