OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,FThe mass rollout of the artificial
OL,7,Fpancreas builds on a successful pilot
OL,8,Fof the technology by NHS England,
OL,9,Fwhich saw 835 adults and children with
OL,10,Ftype 1 diabetes given devices to
OL,11,Fimprove the management of their
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,FEach year, the NHS in England
OL,15,Fcurrently spends around #10 billion a
OL,16,Fyear - around 10% of its entire budget
OL,17,F- on identifying and treating diabetes.
