OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,FDr Clare Hambling, National Clinical
OL,7,FDirector for diabetes said: "This is
OL,8,Fanother example of the NHS leading the
OL,9,Fway in healthcare, rolling out these
OL,10,Fgroundbreaking devices across England
OL,11,Fover the next 5 years.
OL,13,F"This transformative technology holds
OL,14,Fthe power to redefine the lives of
OL,15,Fthose with type 1 diabetes, promising
OL,16,Fa better quality of life as well as
OL,17,Fclinical outcomes.
