OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,F"Type 1 diabetes is an easily missed
OL,7,Fdiagnosis so if you are concerned
OL,8,Fabout symptoms - the 4Ts - going to
OL,9,Fthe Toilet, passing urine more
OL,10,Ffrequently, with Thirst, feeling Tired
OL,11,Fand getting Thinner (loosing weight),
OL,12,Fplease come forward for support."
OL,14,FProfessor Partha Kar, NHS national
OL,15,Fspeciality advisor for diabetes, said:
OL,16,F"The national roll out of Hybrid
OL,17,FClosed Loop systems is great news for
OL,18,Feveryone with type 1 diabetes.
