OL,3,CGroundbreaking 'artificial pancreas'
OL,4,Coffered to type 1 diabetes patients
OL,6,F"The device detects your glucose
OL,7,Flevels, transmits the readings to the
OL,8,Fdelivery system, known as the pump,
OL,9,Fwhich then initiates the process of
OL,10,Fdetermining the required insulin
OL,11,Fdosage.
OL,13,F"This futuristic technology not only
OL,14,Fimproves medical care but also
OL,15,Fenhances the quality of life for those
OL,16,Faffected".
